                    <p> An ogre rescues a princess to reclaim his swamp but ends up finding true love.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card-content">
                    <p>Oh, a love story between an ogre and a princess - how original. Thank goodness for all the bodily function jokes; otherwise, we might have had to focus on actual character development. And who needs that when you have a talking donkey and a villain who's compensating for something? Truly, a cinematic masterpiece for the ages.</p>
