                </div>
                <div class="card-content">
                    <p>Because nothing says "meet the parents" like turning the entire plot into a drawn-out gag reel. Who knew the sequel to an ogre love story would hinge on a makeover and a karaoke party? But hey, at least we get a cat in boots to distract us from the fact that the Fairy Godmother is the real hero here.</p>
                </div>
